1) To Set global user_name
=> Git Config --global user.name "saddam"
2) To set global user_email
=> Git Config --global user.email "saddammohd941@gmail.com"
3) Initiliaze git
=> Git init
4) To add files to tracking area
=> git add (file_name)
5) To add multiple files to tracking area
=> git add .
6) To check Direcotry status
=> git status
7) To Commit files
=> git commit -m "Message"
=> git commit -v
8) git diff commands 
=> git diff
=> git diff --staged
=> git diff --cached
9) To push changes to central
=> git push -u origin master
10) To add remote origin
=> git remote add origin (git_repo_url)
11) To view the remote origin
=> git remote -v
12) To make a copy from central to local
=> git clone (git_repo_url)
13) To pull the latest changes to local
=> git pull (git_repo_url)
14)git branch commands:-
=> git branch (branch_name)  To create branch
=> git checkout (branch name)  To checkout branch
=> git checkout -b (branch name)  to create branch and directiy switch into the branch
=> git branch --list   to list of branches
=> git branch -d (branch name) For deleting branch
=> git push -u origin (branch_name)  To push code to specific branch
15)git log commands:-
=> git log   To view git logs
=> git log --p
=> git log --pretty=oneline
=> git log --pretty=short
=> git log --pretty=full
=> git log --pretty=fuller
=> git log --oneline --graph
=> git log --oneline --graph --all
=> git log --oneline 
=> git log -3   To view last 3 logs
16) merge commands
=> git merge (branch_name)   To merge two branches
=> git brancg --merge        for which branch we merge
=> git branch --no-merge     for which branch we not merged
17) To revert any previous commit
=> git revert (commit_id)
18) Clone one particular branch
=> git clone -b (branch_name) (github_repo_url)
19) Git stash is used to push files to stash memory
=> git stash
20) To view the stash list
=> git stash list
21) To get files out of stash memory
=> git stash pop
22) To get a specific file out of stash memory
=> git stash pop stash{id}
23) to git fetch
=> git fetch origin

